parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp that is accurate to seconds.

parameters.name: Interval
parameters.description:
The time interval between the data entries to return. Unit: seconds. Valid values:

*   **60**: 1 minute
*   **1800**: 30 minutes

parameters.name: NatGatewayId
parameters.description: The ID of the NAT gateway.

parameters.name: SrcPrivateIP
parameters.description: The private IP address of the source.

parameters.name: SrcPublicIP
parameters.description: The public IP address of the source.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The value is a UNIX timestamp. Unit: seconds.
